Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.80,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Wang Xiangzhai used to say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.96,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Zhan Zhuang (Post Standing) is the training of stupid kung fu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.96,0:00:06.20,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,A smart person often fails in hurrying up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.64,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Modern science has certified this
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:11.76,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Muscle memory requires 21 days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.76,0:00:15.16,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,It takes 90 days to truly form an instinctive reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.76,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Those who complain that Zhang Zhuang has no result
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.76,0:00:21.32,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Most of them failed as go fishing 3 days and dry net for 2 days, not persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:24.12,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Isn't not to compare who can stand longer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.36,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,It's the process of talking to your own body
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:28.36,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,When you let go of your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:32.32,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Treat each exercise as a journey of exploring the body
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:35.12,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Naturally, you can surpass a big gap
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.12,0:00:36.96,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,between thinking it to be correct and being wrong once you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.52,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,If you're interested in Zhan Zhuang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.52,0:00:42.76,MyStyle,,0,0,0,,Please contact the teacher, the teacher will teach you
